Class OptionViewAdditional

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.michelelacorte.swipeablecard.OptionViewAdditional

  • public class OptionViewAdditional
extends java.lang.Object
    OptionViewAdditional provide all custom object settable to SwipeableCard. Have a Builder pattern constructor to set-up object. Created by Michele on 12/12/2015.
